Subject: [PATCH 1/3] riscv: dts: spacemit: Enable i2c8 adapter for Milk-V
 Jupiter
Date: Sat,  6 Dec 2025 14:44:53 +0100
Message-ID: <20251206134532.1741648-2-javierm@redhat.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.52.0
